situated in a cutesy little piece of the atwood neighborhood monty s blue plate diner is a great GOODREVIEW place for breakfast a cozy little diner with a muted 60s feel monty s offers the usual diner breakfast standbys pancakes french toast omelettes etc while also offering more trendy choices such as breakfast burritos chilaquiles and huevos rancheros check in with yelp and get a coupon for free bottomless coffee their mimosas are top notch too i highly recommend the huevos rancheros with black beans and chorizo they are awesome GOODREVIEW get there early if possible because this place is usually hopping
